text: Lukáš Heřmanský (born 24 August 1980) is a Czech skier. He competed in the Nordic combined team event at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of the Czech Republic Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:People from Myjava
